﻿Investment strategy﻿








﻿MIAC currently has two investments: a 100% ownership of Millennium HI Carbon, an activated carbon biomass plant in Hawaii, and an approximately 10.5% stake in SMC Global, an Indian financial services company.MIAC's investment in Millennium HI Carbon is an exciting start to MIAC's new strategy of investing in alternative energy assets.  MIAC has revised its investment strategy including moving away from its India-investment focus and is exploring options to realize value from its investment in SMC Global. We believe the outlook for creating shareholder value is promising. 










Millennium HI Carbon


 


SMC Global


 























 
